Package: mixedr2
Title: R-Squared for Mixed Effects Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald G.", "Thomas", email = "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Monte Carlo simulation study comparing R-squared methods
    for linear mixed-effects models. Implements the ADEMP framework to
    evaluate Nakagawa-Schielzeth (2013) and Johnson (2014) methods under
    controlled conditions.
